"{
    "topic": "Sentence Construction & Agreement",
    "topic_hi": "वाक्य निर्माण और सहमति",
    "introduction": {
        "text": "Understanding how the Subject, Verb, and Object work together is the foundation of sentence construction. Number and Person dictate the form of the verb.",
        "text_hi": "Subject, Verb और Object एक साथ कैसे काम करते हैं, यह समझना sentence construction का आधार है। Number और Person verb के रूप को तय करते हैं।",
        "important": "Subject-Verb Agreement is the most critical rule in English grammar. Singular subjects take singular verbs, and plural subjects take plural verbs."
    },
    "teacher_note": "बच्चों, grammar में words को सही order में रखना सबसे ज़रूरी है। अगर order गलत हुआ, तो sentence का अर्थ बदल जाएगा।",
    "rules": [
        {
            "name": "Subject-Verb Agreement",
            "name_hi": "कर्ता-क्रिया सहमति",
            "concept": "The verb must agree with its subject in number (singular/plural) and person (1st, 2nd, 3rd).",
